-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | Benny Lai\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| President Fung\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Kwan Shan]]\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Miss Wong\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | Isabella Wong\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Inspector Jessica Yang\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"2\" |[[Michelle Yeoh]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Panther\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Yuen Wah]]\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Khun Chaibat\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Kenneth Tsang]]\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Chen Wen-Shi Chaibat\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Josephine Koo]]\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| David Chang Fung\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Yu Rongguang]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Inspector Martin Lee Kwong-Ming\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Wakin Chau|Emil Chau]]\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Annie Tsui\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Annie Wu (actress)|Annie Wu]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Jackson Tsui\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[:zh:\u6a13\u5b78\u8ce2|Jackson Liu]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Colonel Gregor Yegorov\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | Yuri Petrov\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Natasha\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Nonna Grishayeva]]\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Mark\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | John Eaves\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Uncle Seven\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | Terry Woo\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Allen\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | Ailen Sit\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" colspan=\"10\" style=\"background:#ddf;\"| '''Reboot Series'''\n|-\n|Senior Inspector Chan Kwok-Wing\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | Jackie Chan\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Detective Frank Cheng Siu-Fung\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Nicholas Tse]]\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Sun Ho-Yee\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Charlie Young (actress)|Charlie Yeung]]\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Officer Sa Sa\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Charlene Choi]]\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Joe Kwan\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Daniel Wu]]\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Commander Chiu Chan\n| colspan=\"5\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | Yu Rongguang\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n|-\n| Detective Zhong Wen\n| colspan=\"6\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | Jackie Chan\n|-\n| Miao Miao\n| colspan=\"6\" style=\"background-color:#D3D3D3;\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" | [[Jing Tian]]\n|-\n| Wu Jiang\n|